title: The English Home - May 2014  UK
description:
The English Home - May 2014  UK

148 Pages | True PDF | English | 49 MB 


Each issue showcases a blend of classic, elegant and country homes alongside insights from world-acclaimed designers, architects and industry experts. We also showcase evocative features on quintessentially English pastimes and pursuits, seasonal recipes and life at home. The result is an engaging, insightful read to refer to again and again.
